  "$description": "Inkwell color system v2.1. Derived from objectcore.ai/agents (extracted 2026-07-02). Primitives unchanged from v1; semantic layer re-cut so every documented text pairing meets WCAG AAA (SC 1.4.6, >=7:1). 'paper' = light, 'ink' = dark. v2.1 adds four wardrobe themes (study, kiln, arboretum, nocturne); every documented pairing in every theme meets AAA. v2.2 adds --border-input (>=3:1, WCAG 1.4.11) to every theme and separates lamps/selected fills from tinted canvases."
